 Hide Tallow's products manufactured?","answer":"<p>All of our products are proudly manufactured in the <strong>USA<\/strong>. We handle everything in small batches—from rendering and purifying to whipping and pouring—to ensure every jar meets our high standards for ancestral skin nutrition.<\/p>"}},"faq_item_VAtapk":{"type":"faq_item","settings":{"question":"Where does Hide Tallow Source their Tallow?","answer":"<p>We believe the quality of the tallow is only as good as the life of the animal. We meticulously source our suet from trusted regenerative farmers across the United States who prioritize soil health and animal welfare. Currently, our 100% grass-fed and finished tallow is sourced from a<strong>small family farm in Delaware<\/strong>, ensuring we use only the highest nutrient-density suet available for your skin.<\/p>"}},"faq_item_gLBnFV":{"type":"faq_item","settings":{"question":"How long of a shelf life do Hide Tallow products have?","answer":"<p>Because our tallow is meticulously purified and contains zero water or synthetic fillers, it is naturally shelf-stable. Our products have a shelf life of <strong>12 months <\/strong>from the date of opening. <\/p><p>To maintain maximum nutrient density, we recommend storing your jars in a cool, dry place and keeping them out of direct sunlight.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["faq_item_jCAnKr","faq_item_9mLgD4","faq_item_VAtapk","faq_item_gLBnFV"],"name":"HT FAQ Customizable","settings":{"main_title":"FAQs","main_subtext":"Everything you need to know about Hide Tallow.","max_width":900,"margin_top":15,"margin_bottom":25,"color_section_bg":"#ffffff","color_heading":"#0e3a27","color_subheading":"#4a4a4a","color_question_bg":"#f9faf8","color_question_text":"#0e3a27","color_answer_bg":"#ffffff","color_body_text":"#333333","color_border":"#e5e7e2","color_active_border":"#0e3a27","title_size":42,"subheading_size":14,"header_spacing":50,"question_size":16,"body_size":12,"padding_y":25,"padding_x":30,"item_gap":16,"border_radius